{"tid":2117854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：若選舉如期舉行 選民要戴口罩和即棄手套投票 確診患者將無法投票","createTime":"2020-07-21T06:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T10:26:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":87,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"10bd469b618ff17fc2e741151f929e5482d6cb7f","tid":2117854,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"政制局：會及早制訂各種預案 政制及內地事務局表示，考慮到疫情預計在短期內不會消退，會與食物及衛生局、衛生防護中心密切注視疫情發展，不斷評估疫情對立法會換屆選舉的影響，及早制訂各種預案。 <br />\n<br />\n根據當局五月提交予立法會的文件，若果選舉如期舉行，選民要戴口罩和即棄手套投票，有發燒徵狀的選民會去特別投票間投票，每次用完會消毒。 <br />\n<br />\n政府亦考慮是否容許正接受強制檢疫的選民暫時外出投票，當局會考慮在五個地方選區各指定一個投票站，或在個別檢疫中心設立投票站。至於確診患者就無法投票，醫院不會設立特別票站，亦不會分發選票到每張病床。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348179&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=66852d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348179</a>"},{"pid":"5b372a0bcf48925664385bb5e0f607e7cace6558","tid":2117854,"uid":160227,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"確診者無法投票<br />\n<br />\n但係搬咗去支那喺香港冇居住證明嘅人可以投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748aba1d21050b0d6eb6287d7cdddfe86f2e8012","tid":2117854,"uid":132587,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7277c57b67a5589d29c63c01fcc783ff83a4c037","tid":2117854,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faa3f2462962f6da2d168f2977b22d9132be117","tid":2117854,"uid":25468,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"星加坡幾萬人確診都如期選舉 , 香港2千人就收皮唔選 ?<br />\n<br />\n幾時到美國押後大選 ?"},{"pid":"5c934ccf5129060d260cff92cdc6d644fb2ab660","tid":2117854,"uid":258706,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gfN5Ga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gfN5Ga.jpg&h=1e131b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【劭勸行動】<br />\n日期 📆 : 7月20日-31日 (選舉提名期結束之日)<br />\n地點 📍 : 任何適合傾計、劭勸手足的地方<br />\n<br />\n行動內容 💬 ：<br />\n劭勸、勉勵並支持各界別合資格、有堅定意志的手足參選功能組別 👏 避免親中派自動當選、壟斷 👎 <br />\n<br />\n總目的 🚩 ：<br />\n增加35+成事之機會 ✔ 令更多手足透過功能組別取得議席並於立法會內以任何方式與權力要求政府落實五大訴求、否決非&quot;港人優先&quot;之議案 <br />\n<br />\n方式 👉 ：深情對話、傾電話、Message對方...等任何方式<br />\n<br />\n討論：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2116545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2116545</a><br />\nTG： <a href=\"http://t.me/AntiFCWalkover\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiFCWalkover&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b9f4f267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/AntiFCWalkover</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呢12個界别要人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勸合資格嘅朋友、家人、同事參選吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"94d0fecca1481c2c4e2bee06348e7548f017c66b","tid":2117854,"uid":88743,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:33:58.000Z","msg":"慶回歸群組無得投票<br />\n唔公平<br />\n投票取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cc551da4513aa4faeb50f030f57bfa251ec35d","tid":2117854,"uid":121197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"而家連投票權都剝奪埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b100114b7a68d23931d1807b45fea52f37228f91","tid":2117854,"uid":20563,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"確診者唔俾投票<br />\n<br />\n就算坐緊監或者係傷殘，甚至唔係住香港既藍絲都可以投"},{"pid":"7dd01fc1a3d30994cbbb85ff6b8105049e37b101","tid":2117854,"uid":50740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T06:35:25.000Z"